{
  "name": "Director Holt",
  "type": "npc",
  "img": "icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The VP of Security Operations at Meridian Consolidated, a defense contractor with fingers in every government contract in the region. Holt has no powers and no combat training, but he commands a private army, controls the city's surveillance infrastructure, and has the ear of three city council members. He views paragons as an unregulated liability and is building a legal and political framework to bring them under corporate control. He is the most dangerous kind of villain: patient, legitimate, and entirely correct that nobody can arrest him.</p>",
